{"tid":2283110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登防疫顧問建議全國封鎖6周  聯邦政府可以透過發債繳付勞工薪資","createTime":"2020-11-12T10:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T15:52:15.000Z","uid":14918,"like":17,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"eb5d413a7c2d26ec72a49689f32ab3cbd67ec88f","tid":2283110,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"Biden's COVID chief says the US should go into a total national lockdown for six WEEKS to avoid 'virus hell' and the federal government can borrow to pay workers while country is shutdown <br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人拜登的抗疫顧問 Michael Osterholm 博士周三 (11 日) 表示，實施全國封鎖四到六周有助控制疫情，他建議由政府負擔人民封鎖期間失去的薪資，讓經濟在疫苗獲准上市並開始分發之前運作無虞，而拜登政府可以透過舉債支應資金需求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被任命為拜登抗疫諮詢委員會成員的 Osterholm 形容，美國疫情正要進入「地獄」階段，他對 CNBC 說：「現在連逼近疫情高峰都還談不上，而美國的醫療體系已經超載。未來三到四個月將是到目前為止，疫情最黑暗的時刻。」<br />\n<br />\n目前美國每日確診人數平均超過 12 萬人，每日住院人數創新高，達到 61964 人。<br />\n<br />\nOsterholm 另外接受 Yahoo 財經訪問時表示，在疫苗問世之前，全國封鎖措施可以把每日新增病例和住院人數降到可控制的水準，「我們可以透過方案負擔勞工流失的薪資、中小企業或地方政府的損失。能做到這一點，我們就能封鎖四到六個禮拜。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4542142\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4542142&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=5a2b49a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4542142</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8939863/Bidens-coronavirus-advisor-says-U-S-national-lockdown-4-6-weeks.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8939863%2FBidens-coronavirus-advisor-says-U-S-national-lockdown-4-6-weeks.html&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=408c67f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8939863/Bidens-coronavirus-advisor-says-U-S-national-lockdown-4-6-weeks.html</a>"},{"pid":"3b467ef4686e74e200048e0922a8f254c21f714d","tid":2283110,"uid":79117,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"361383488fffaf91dca8e1bc3ba6c4d963cc1abe","tid":2283110,"uid":103207,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"鎖完6星期再爆咁點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5d0faeeac8fbda084c97aa5e163a4281726bc6","tid":2283110,"uid":196924,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:26:29.000Z","msg":"發債 -&gt; 支那買  -&gt; 感謝支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51b7d4c3b61208e946cc3b0d28926cdd6b21db2","tid":2283110,"uid":290393,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"eb5d413a7c2d26ec72a49689f32ab3cbd67ec88f","tid":2283110,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"Biden's COVID chief says the US should go into a total national lockdown for six WEEKS to avoid 'virus hell' and the federal government can borrow to pay workers while country is shutdown <br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人拜登的抗疫顧問 Michael Osterholm 博士周三 (11 日) 表示，實施全國封鎖四到六周有助控制疫情，他建議由政府負擔人民封鎖期間失去的薪資，讓經濟在疫苗獲准上市並開始分發之前運作無虞，而拜登政府可以透過舉債支應資金需求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被任命為拜登抗疫諮詢委員會成員的 Osterholm 形容，美國疫情正要進入「地獄」階段，他對 CNBC 說：「現在連逼近疫情高峰都還談不上，而美國的醫療體系已經超載。未來三到四個月將是到目前為止，疫情最黑暗的時刻。」<br />\n<br />\n目前美國每日確診人數平均超過 12 萬人，每日住院人數創新高，達到 61964 人。<br />\n<br />\nOsterholm 另外接受 Yahoo 財經訪問時表示，在疫苗問世之前，全國封鎖措施可以把每日新增病例和住院人數降到可控制的水準，「我們可以透過方案負擔勞工流失的薪資、中小企業或地方政府的損失。能做到這一點，我們就能封鎖四到六個禮拜。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass